ActionMailerCacheDelivery
========================

Currently ActionMailer only supports :test, :smtp & :sendmail delivery methods.
This plugin enhances ActionMailer to support use temporary cache file in :test method,
making them available to other processes.

Installation
============

  #$ cd RAILS_ROOT
  #$ ./script/plugin install git://github.com/guillaumegentil/action_mailer_cache_delivery.git

